00:11:27,900 --> 00:11:30,660
They’re all washed, let's keep going.

264
00:11:30,660 --> 00:11:32,500
Okay, everyone. 1, 2, 3.

265
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:34,780
Just so you know, the soda water's limited.

266
00:11:36,180 --> 00:11:37,660
Ah, this is enough.

267
00:11:38,180 --> 00:11:39,260
Soda water's limited!

268
00:11:39,260 --> 00:11:40,420
We have water.

269
00:11:41,060 --> 00:11:42,420
Ah.

270
00:11:43,540 --> 00:11:46,620
-Stop playing, Kong, lemons are limited.
-Can I taste one? I want to know how it tastes.

271
00:11:46,620 --> 00:11:48,340
Uh, take another one, take another!

272
00:11:48,340 --> 00:11:49,540
That's too much.

273
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:54,020
There's more.

274
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:55,820
Wait, why does it look like this?

275
00:11:56,300 --> 00:11:58,420
It's not what I imagined!

276
00:11:59,940 --> 00:12:03,580
Oh, it's not mixed evenly yet.

277
00:12:09,860 --> 00:12:10,900
Ugh.

278
00:12:11,260 --> 00:12:13,620
