-Hey.

279
00:12:13,620 --> 00:12:15,980
I think we still have time left.

280
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:20,020
Really? The way to cut fruit.

281
00:12:20,860 --> 00:12:23,820
-I don't know. They gave me 15 minutes.
-Auau.

282
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:26,220
And I'm a beginner.

283
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:28,820
See? I'm pretty good!

284
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:31,300
Look! We did it!

285
00:12:31,300 --> 00:12:32,860
It's really a non-alcoholic cocktail, Auau!

286
00:12:32,860 --> 00:12:34,340
-Yes.
-Then why did you mix this?

287
00:12:34,340 --> 00:12:35,220
Wow.

288
00:12:35,980 --> 00:12:38,060
See? It really looks like a non-alcoholic cocktail!

289
00:12:38,060 --> 00:12:39,260
I'll drink that one later.

290
00:12:39,260 --> 00:12:40,220
I'm going to...

291
00:12:40,220 --> 00:12:43,340
-I don't know how to cut it, guys.
-Time is limited.

292
00:12:43,340 --> 00:12:46,860
