Auau, don't tell me you're just tossing it in like that!

293
00:12:46,860 --> 00:12:49,460
No, I meant we should squeeze the juice out.

294
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:51,460
Can I say no to this?

295
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:53,780
We need to squeeze the juice.

296
00:12:53,780 --> 00:12:55,420
That's it. Done.

297
00:12:55,420 --> 00:12:56,620
Not yet.

298
00:12:56,620 --> 00:12:58,940
Ah, then let's make the most of the time left!

299
00:12:58,940 --> 00:13:00,380
Look here.

300
00:13:00,380 --> 00:13:03,060
Auau, can you hold these for me?

301
00:13:03,060 --> 00:13:04,420
